<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">The syllogism is:</p>
<ol style=3D"list-style-type: decimal; padding-left: 40px; margin: 16px 0;"=
>=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Every bad thing that a public company=
 does <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.com/click/32347622.263=
413/aHR0cHM6Ly93d3cuYmxvb21iZXJnLmNvbS9vcGluaW9uL2FydGljbGVzLzIwMjEtMDItMDM=
vZ29sZG1hbi1zYWNocy1nb2VzLXRvLXN1cHJlbWUtY291cnQtaGVkZ2UtZnVuZHMtd29uLW9uLW=
dhbWVzdG9wLWtrcG9lNndzP2NtcGlkPUJCRDA4MDkyM19NT05FWVNUVUZGJnV0bV9tZWRpdW09Z=
W1haWwmdXRtX3NvdXJjZT1uZXdzbGV0dGVyJnV0bV90ZXJtPTIzMDgwOSZ1dG1fY2FtcGFpZ249=
bW9uZXlzdHVmZg/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cBc5e11ec5" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" it=
emscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #000000; text-decor=
ation: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-bottom-color: #000=
000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;"> is securities fr=
aud</a>: The company did the bad thing, it didn=E2=80=99t tell shareholders=
 about it in advance, the shareholders bought the stock not knowing about t=
he bad thing, and when they learned of it they felt defrauded.</li>=09<li s=
tyle=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">In the US, politics are both=C2=A0polarized an=
d totalizing: Everything that everyone does has some political valence, and=
 some people will think it is bad while others will think it is good.</li>=
=09<li style=3D"margin-bottom: 5px;">Therefore everything that a public com=
pany does=C2=A0<em>strikes someone as bad</em>, and <em>is therefore securi=
ties fraud</em>.</li>
</ol>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">I don=E2=80=99t make the rules! I mean, I gues=
s I did kind of make up the rule =E2=80=9Ceverything is securities fraud,=
=E2=80=9D but only as a description of what I have observed in reality. I d=
on=E2=80=99t like it. But <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloombergbusiness.co=
m/click/32347622.263413/aHR0cHM6Ly9uZXdzLmJsb29tYmVyZ2xhdy5jb20vYnVzaW5lc3M=
tYW5kLXByYWN0aWNlL2V4LXRydW1wLW9mZmljaWFscy1zdWUtdGFyZ2V0LWFsbGVnaW5nLXByaW=
RlLW1vbnRoLWludmVzdG9yLXJpc2s/607f07ceef4b8524a319a23cB9e93d59b" itemprop=
=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope" target=3D"_blank" style=3D"color: #0=
00000; text-decoration: none !important; border-bottom-width: 1px; border-b=
ottom-color: #000000; border-bottom-style: solid; background-color: #ccc;">=
  here you go</a>:</p>
<blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Target is facing a lawsuit from former Trump o=
fficials who claim the retailer misled investors about financial risks from=
 LGBTQ Pride marketing that brought a conservative backlash costing shareho=
lders billions of dollars.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">America First Legal Foundation, led by former =
senior Trump adviser Stephen Miller, filed the lawsuit against Target Corp.=
 on behalf of a company shareholder Tuesday in federal court in Florida. Ta=
rget in May sold LGBTQ-themed merchandise that drew the retailer into the U=
S culture wars alongside Bud Light maker Anheuser-Busch InBev NV and other =
companies.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Some customers condemned Target=E2=80=99s merc=
handising of clothing and products intended for Pride Month in June, which =
celebrates lesbian, gay, bisexual and transgender people. The retailer then=
 said it was pulling some items after threats against employees, garnering =
additional rebukes from customers angered by its retreat.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Target lost $10 billion in market valuation be=
tween May 18 and 28, as it failed to oversee the risks of ESG initiatives, =
according to America First Legal=E2=80=99s complaint filed in the US Distri=
ct Court for the Middle District of Florida.</p>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">=E2=80=9CNo rational board of directors or man=
agement of a retailer with a core customer base of working families would h=
ave approved such a nationwide campaign,=E2=80=9D America First Legal said =
in the complaint. =E2=80=9CNonetheless, Target=E2=80=99s officials pursued.=
=E2=80=9D</p>
</blockquote>
<p style=3D"margin: 16px 0;">Here is <a href=3D"https://link.mail.bloomberg=
business.com/click/32347622.263413/aHR0cHM6Ly9hYm91dGJsYXcuY29tLzlTcA/607f0=
7ceef4b8524a319a23cBaf4d30d3" itemprop=3D"StoryLink" itemscope=3D"itemscope=
